0. git clone https://github.com/mirkowang/dotfiles

1. requirements:
    1.0: iterm2, homebrew, oh-my-zsh
        1.0.1: /bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"
        1.0.2: sh -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)"
    1.1: fonts
        1.1.1: OperatorMono for ascii 
        1.1.2: font-hack-nerd-font for non-ascii (brew install font-hack-nerd-font) 
        1.1.3: setup for non-ascii in iterm2
    1.2: colorscheme
        1.2.1: base16-google-light.itermcolors
    1.3: tools
        1.3.1: brew install neovim tmux git wget npm (npm is required for jsonls and yamlls)

2. setup (alias, zshr, rbenv, pyenv)
    2.0: chmod +x setup & ./setup
    2.1: enable italic text && turn off "Show mark indicators" for iterm2
    2.2: tic -x tmux/tmux-256color.terminfo  (setup tmux to enable italic text)
    2.3: silent bell (!!!)

3. programming requirements
    3.0: lua (lua_ls for lsp, luacheck for lint, stylua for format)
        3.0.0: installed by Mason

    3.1: python (pylsp for lsp, installed by mason, ruff for lint, ruff-format for format)
        3.1.0: pyenv install 3.10
        3.1.2: pip3 install ruff

    3.2: ruby (ruby-lsp for lsp, rubocop for ruby lint & format, erb-lint/erb-formatter for eruby lint/format)
        3.2.0: rbenv install 3.3.1 & rbenv global 3.3.1
        3.2.1: gem install rubocop erb_lint erb-formatter

4. install
    5.0: chmod +x install && ./install


